  <brief_title>Chemical Ice Packs for Cooling Hyperthermic Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial Assessing Effectiveness of Chemical Cold Packs Used on Various Skin Surfaces for Cooling Hyperthermic Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
